Dr. Judy Mikovits pHd joins Gary Franchi on the Next News Network. She has published 51 scientific papers in peer-reviewed journals and was a Postdoctoral Scholar in Molecular Virology at the Laboratory of Genomic Diversity, National Cancer Institute. She has also been a target of Dr. Anthony Fauci twice, however recently the tables have turned and sights are on Fauci as his motives and miscalculations could be exposed on a global stage. Today we investigate just how many bodies lie in the wake of his rise to the top of the National Institute of Health. ----------------------------------
